<item>
 <title>brokers</title>
 <link>https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/node/128</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-page-banner field-type-image field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Page Banner:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/sites/default/files/Brokers_banner_0.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1468&quot; height=&quot;579&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-claims-requirement-body field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Banner Content:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;captions&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-8&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;caption-box&quot;&gt;
            &lt;h1&gt;Brokers&lt;/h1&gt;
          &lt;!--  &lt;h2&gt;WAPIC, preferred among brokers&lt;/h2&gt; --&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Endearing relationships are key to our success.&lt;br&gt; Excellence and professionalism guide our engagement with all brokers.&lt;/p&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;caption-buttons single&quot;&gt;
           &lt;!--   &lt;a href=&quot;https://mywapic.wapic.com/branch/login&quot;&lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;btn button_purple2&quot;&gt;LOGIN&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/a&gt; --&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-accordion-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;After Banner Content:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt; Brokers appreciate doing business with Wapic because of our reputation for excellence and our robust business portfolio. We welcome reputable brokers and look forward to assisting them meet their clients’ varied needs. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-press-title field-type-text field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Title:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;MOTOR VEHICLE INSURANCE&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;MARINE CARGO&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-press-release-body field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Content:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt; &lt;h4&gt;Product Brief:&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a product that pays for damages to your vehicle as a result of theft, accident and fire. It comes in 3 variants namely Moov (Third Party), Moov Plus (Third Party, Fire and theft), Moov Prestige (Comprehensive) and Moov Luxury (Comprehensive)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;

  &lt;h4&gt;Target Market:&lt;/h4&gt;Corporations&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Benefits&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Covers Third party bodily injury &amp;amp; death – unlimited&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Unlimited cover for accidental bodily injury or death of third party&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Covers cost of repairs to own vehicle if damaged by fire&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Indemnifies you in case vehicle is stolen&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Towing limit: N10,000.00&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Insured’s personal accident benefits: a limit of N100,000.00&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Loss of personal effect up to N30,000.00&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Authorized repair limit up to N50,000.00&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Third party property damage up to N2million&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Fire damage to the insured vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Theft &amp;amp; Accidental damage of the vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Excess buyback: free&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Flat depreciation rate&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Riot, strike &amp;amp; civil commotion (RSCC): Free&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Free tracker if vehicle value is N3million and above&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Passenger liability: N75,000 per person &amp;amp; N350,000 per vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Repair caused by accidental damage is paid for by insurer&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Nil depreciation on total write off for a brand new vehicle of less than six months&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;No Claim Bonus of 2.5% payable after 2nd year of renewal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Policy Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Completed proposal form&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Copy of vehicle license&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Proof of ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Claims Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Repair estimate from a certified mechanic&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Clear photographs of the damaged vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Police report in the event of injury or death of a third party&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Product Brief:&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This policy covers the shipment of consignment for one single voyage after which the contract terminates. The certificate is issued by the underwriter per request from client.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Target Market:&lt;/h4&gt; Importers&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
	&lt;h4&gt;Benefits&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Protects you from footing the bill of loss/damage of goods in the cargo&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Provides unlimited cover for third party property loss&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Cover is warehouse-to-warehouse; from the time the goods leave the seller to the place of storage at the final destination&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Wapic offers an annual open cargo policy which automatically insures your shipments on set terms, conditions and rate without the need to contact us each time.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;ship being stranded, grounded, sunk or capsized&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;overturning or derailment of other land transport&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;collision of the ship or other form of transport with any external object&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;General Average &amp;amp; Jettison&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Policy Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Copy of Form M&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Country of origin/destination&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Proforma Invoice&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;KYC Documentation&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Claims Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Original policy or certificate of insurance&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Original or copy shipping invoice, together with shipping specification and/or weight notes.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Original Bill of Laden and/or other contract of carriage&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Survey report or other documentary evidence to show the extent of the loss or damage&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Landing account and weight notes at final destination.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Discrepancy certificate&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Correspondence exchanged with the Carriers and other parties regarding their liability for the loss or damage&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-leadership-photo field-type-image field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Image:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/sites/default/files/Motor-Vehicle-Insurance_1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;350&quot; height=&quot;253&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/sites/default/files/marin_cargo_1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;350&quot; height=&quot;253&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
