 <title>partners</title>
 <link>https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/node/127</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-page-banner field-type-image field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Page Banner:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/sites/default/files/Partners_Banner.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1200&quot; height=&quot;429&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-claims-requirement-body field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Banner Content:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;captions&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-8&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;caption-box&quot;&gt;
            &lt;h1&gt;Partners&lt;/h1&gt;
           &lt;!-- &lt;h2&gt;With our partners we do&lt;/h2&gt; --&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Partners portal coming soon&lt;/p&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;caption-buttons single&quot;&gt;
            &lt;a href=&quot;https://askniid.org&quot;&gt;  &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;btn button_purple2&quot;&gt;Verify Your Policy&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-accordion-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;After Banner Content:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;  As partners, our watchword is teamwork; we seek energetic and innovative partners with valuable experience working with insurance companies, who are passionate about excellent customer service regardless of the market segment in which they operate.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-press-title field-type-text field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Title:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;MOOV PRESTIGE&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;SMART LIFE PLUS&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-press-release-body field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Body:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Product Brief:&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is an insurance product that pays for damages to your vehicle as a result of theft, accident or fire. It also covers third party damages for which you are liable. With this policy, the cost of replacing or repairing your vehicle is covered no matter who is at fault. If needed, you can also buy additional features such as excess buy-back or increased third party along with the standard features of the product.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Target Market:&lt;/h4&gt; Individuals/corporations&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
	&lt;h4&gt;Benefits&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers third party property damage&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers third party bodily injury &amp;amp; death (Unlimited)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers cost of repairs caused by fire damage&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers cost of repairs for own damage&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Indemnifies in case of theft&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Nil depreciation on total write off for a brand new vehicle of less than six months&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No-Claim Bonus of 2.5% payable after 2nd year of renewal&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Third party property damage (up to N1million)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Third party bodily injury and death (Unlimited)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers loss from fire damage to the insured vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers theft of the vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Covers accidental damage to insured&#039;s vehicle (up to total value of vehicle)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Includes towing limit (up to N10,000.00)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Personal accident benefits for the insured (up to a limit of N20,000)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Loss of personal effects (up to a limit of N10,000)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Authorised repair limit (up to N40,000)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Free tracker for vehicle valued N4million and above&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Passenger liability (N75,000 per person and a maximum of N350,000 per vehicle)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Policy deductibles/excess applies&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Policy Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Complete the application process&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Effect premium payment&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Observe the terms and conditions outlined in the Policy Document&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;h4&gt;Claims Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Completed proposal form&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Proof of ownership&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Vehicle License&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Acceptable proof of identification&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;h4&gt;Product Brief:&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Wapic Smart Life+ Plan is an insurance solution that provides you the opportunity of systematically accumulating funds toward meeting short-term obligations and emergencies with an embedded free life cover. Yes, FREE life cover!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;

  &lt;h4&gt;Target Market:&lt;/h4&gt;Individuals/Employees&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Benefits&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Enjoy FREE life cover of up to N2 million while saving toward financial goal&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No underwriting for your convenience&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Flexible but high return on investment&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Vehicle toward achieving short term financial goals and needs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Succour in the event of demise&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Premiums are tax deductible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Minimum annual contribution: N60,000&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Minimum duration: 1 year&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Entry age: 18-54 years&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Part withdrawal: up to 85% of accumulated principal; however, interest will be affected&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Premium payment frequency: Flexible&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Return on investment: Index linked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;Policy Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Complete the application form&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Effect premium payment&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Observe the terms and conditions outlined in the policy document.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-leadership-photo field-type-image field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Image:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/sites/default/files/Moov_Prestige_0.jpg&quot; width=&quot;350&quot; height=&quot;234&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/Ghana/sites/default/files/Smart_Life_Plus_0.jpg&quot; width=&quot;350&quot; height=&quot;234&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
